g>by Harvard Medical School!\u200b<\/p><p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\">Read more <a href=\"https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/posts\/harvard-medical-school_serendipity-played-a-part-in-ella-perrault-activity-7295886464251224064-TB7_?utm_source=share&amp;utm_medium=member_desktop&amp;rcm=ACoAAASma3ABcXC5-7kQgZIxkwCnVZIyXA1VbuU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">here<\/span><\/a>!<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d368eac e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"d368eac\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-179ae7d elementor-widget__width-auto elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"179ae7d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https:\/\/whwanglab.mgh.harvard.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/highlight2-1-scaled-2.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-3095\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/whwanglab.mgh.harvard.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/highlight2-1-scaled-2.jpeg 2560w, https:\/\/whwanglab.mgh.harvard.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/highlight2-1-scaled-2-300x200.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/whwanglab.mgh.harvard.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/highlight2-1-scaled-2-1024x683.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/whwanglab.mgh.harvard.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/highlight2-1-scaled-2-768x512.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/whwanglab.mgh.harvard.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/highlight2-1-scaled-2-1536x1024.jpeg 1536w, https:\/\/whwanglab.mgh.harvard.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/highlight2-1-scaled-2-2048x1366.jpeg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-33b2025 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"33b2025\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c412e5d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c412e5d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The <strong>Hwang Laboratory<\/strong> (or <strong>LaSSO Research Group<\/strong>) has a deep interest in the immense phenotypic, temporal and spatial heterogeneity of tumor ecosystems and the many insights that can only be gleaned by studying these systems at the level of their individual components\u2014single molecules or cells. Research in the Hwang Laboratory is focused on studying tumor-stroma interactions at unprecedented resolution through the development and application of techniques in single-cell and spatial biology, multiplexed imaging, and functional genetic screens to patient-derived specimens, organoids, and mouse models to elucidate mechanisms of:<\/p><ul><li>Therapeutic resistance mediated by genetic, epigenetic, and phenotypic factors including cell state plasticity<\/li><li>Treatment-mediated remodeling of the spatial microarchitecture of tumors and underlying cancer cell-stromal interactions<\/li><li>Tumor-nerve crosstalk, which plays a critical role in the pathophysiology and morbidity of many malignancies but remains understudied<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cbc92f3 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"cbc92f3\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b2b15d1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b2b15d1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Media<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bec387a e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"bec387a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-92508a7 e-con-full press-grid e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"92508a7\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-239079e e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"239079e\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6e0b07a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"6e0b07a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1ca70e9 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1ca70e9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.biopharmadive.com\/news\/cancer-pain-drugs-research-opioid-alternatives\/760463\/\">Cancer patients are living longer than ever. Pain drugmakers haven\u2019t kept up.<\/a><br \/><span class=\"press-outlet\"><em>BioPharma Dive \u2022 2025<\/em><\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3144f12 e-con-full press-img e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"3144f12\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"eleme